duties_responsibilities.duty: Provide dental services to patients with the support of the dental team
Utilize DentaPro software and digital x-ray and Panorex units for diagnostic purposes
Complete yearly OSHA and HIPPA and Emergency Management training to ensure compliance
Manage patient base primarily consisting of ages 3-21 and up to 30% adult population
Oversee an office flow with an average of 10-12 operative patients and 20-25 hygiene patients

education_certification.credential: DDS/DMD from a dental education program accredited by the Commission on Dental Accreditation
Current, valid license to practice dentistry in states where providing care or eligible for licensure
Other certifications as required - CPR, DEA, etc.
Nitrous Oxide certification (only LA, MS, DC, TX, MA)
